Follow [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) for cold-start and validation lanes.

- Docs / config → `bun run validate:changed -- <path>` or `bun run audit:self`
- Skill body → `bun run audit:skills` (path-scoped validate exits non-zero)
- TypeScript → `bun test` + `bun run typecheck` + `bun run build`
